title: April 25/ World Malaria Day | Bill Gates pledges Billions to Vaccines |
description:
Today the 25/April is World Malaria Day.
The first batch of experimental Malaria vaccines heads for the continent of Africa where some 360,000 children per year in three African countries namely Malawi, Ghana and Kenya will be given the vaccine as part of a pilot project by the World Health Organization.
